title: The DDFP - Top 100 reaction podcast No. 40-31
itunes:title: The DDFP - Top 100 reaction podcast No. 40-31
description:
Dave and Rank tackle the next 10 players unveiled in the Top 100 players of 2010 list.  The two are up-in-arms over the player at No. 32 and another guard at No. 34.   Overall, it's a thin slice of heaven - unless you're player No. 32 or 34.
